===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*m/s-glak ~ m-glaŋ||cold; freeze}}. Cognate with {{och-l|霜|frost}}, {{cog|bo|གྲང་||cold}}. According to {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}}, this etymon seems to have a wider distribution: Compare Austroasiatic {{cog|khr|raŋga||cold; freeze}}, {{cog|km|រងា||cold}}.

A derivative is probably {{och-l|凔|cold}}. A vocalic variant is {{och-l|冷|cold}}.

